<p>
<lb n="1"/>svastiśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakavarṣaṁbulu
<lb n="2"/>1315 Agunēṁṭi śrīmu
<lb n="3" break="no"/>khasaṁvatsara vaiśākha śu 5 gu
<lb n="4"/>poraṇūri śrībhāvanārā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>yaṇa perumāḷlakunu kuṁ
<lb n="6" break="no"/>maṁgūri Aśēṣavidvanmahājanā
<lb n="7" break="no"/>lacēta laṁkapalli bhāvani vāri
<lb n="8"/>taṁmulu narahari teluṁga
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ri kālōcitamūlyamu veṭṭi
<lb n="10"/>vilcikoni tama tallidaṁḍrula
<lb n="11" break="no"/>kuṁ buṇyamugānu dhāravō
<lb n="12" break="no"/>si yiccina vritti kuṁmaṁgū
<lb n="13" break="no"/>ri Uttarābhāgāna selamāsakamma
<lb n="14" break="no"/>ceṟuvu dakṣiṇa<unclear>ṁ</unclear> na kha 1 na 10 kā
<lb n="15" break="no"/>ṁkaṟava na 10 Ācaṁdrārkkamukānu
<lb n="16"/>Icciri <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

<p>1. At the top are cut the figures of a sun, crescent, conch, discus and a <hi rend="italic">Garuḍa</hi> saluting an image.</p>

